name: Josie Rizal
bio: Ever since she was very young, Josie had a reputation for being a crybaby. Josie's parents, who were big fans of martial arts, insisted that she begin training. Despite her reluctance at first, Josie was eager to live up to her parents' expectations, and became a top-notch kick-boxer - however, her fighting prowess did not rid her of her sensitive disposition.
